---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

---

<Layout title="Now">
	<div
    class="min-h-screen py-10 md:px-5 px-2 flex flex-col gap-5"
    style="background-color: #ececaa;"
  >
  <main class="min-h-screen max-w-3xl mx-auto py-16 px-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6 text-center">
        <i class="bi bi-clock-history text-indigo-600"></i> What I'm Doing Now
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-center mb-12 text-gray-600">
        A snapshot of my current projects, passions, and weekend experiments.
      </p>

      <ul class="space-y-6">
        <li class="border-2 border-black rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] hover:shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transition-all bg-white p-6">
          <i class="bi bi-microscope text-pink-500 text-2xl mr-2"></i>
          <strong>Researcher in Histology & Embryology</strong> — writing a scientific project on how <em>TMAO</em> affects ovarian granulosa cells.
        </li>

        <li class="border-2 border-black rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] hover:shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transition-all bg-white p-6">
          <i class="bi bi-phone text-green-500 text-2xl mr-2"></i>
          Developing an <strong>Angular + Ionic + Firebase</strong> app: <a href="https://askhisto.web.app" target="_blank" class="hover:font-bold"><em>AskHisto</em></a>, a histology quiz tool for students.
        </li>

        <li class="border-2 border-black rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] hover:shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transition-all bg-white p-6">
          <i class="bi bi-cube text-purple-600 text-2xl mr-2"></i>
          Learning <strong>Blender</strong> for a potential embryology learning platform with interactive 3D content.
        </li>

        <li class="border-2 border-black rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] hover:shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transition-all bg-white p-6">
          <i class="bi bi-code-slash text-blue-500 text-2xl mr-2"></i>
          Wrapping up unfinished projects — like this portfolio website and <a href="https://saba-design.netlify.app/" target="_blank" class="hover:font-bold">my sister’s portfolio page</a>.
        </li>

        <li class="border-2 border-black rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] hover:shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transition-all bg-white p-6">
          <i class="bi bi-emoji-smile text-yellow-500 text-2xl mr-2"></i>
          Joyfully raising my <strong>3-year-old toddler</strong>.
        </li>

        <li class="border-2 border-black rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] hover:shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transition-all bg-white p-6">
          <i class="bi bi-leaf text-green-600 text-2xl mr-2"></i>
          Doing my best to <strong>avoid animal products</strong> whenever possible.
        </li>

        <li class="border-2 border-black rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] hover:shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transition-all bg-white p-6">
          <i class="bi bi-droplet-half text-cyan-500 text-2xl mr-2"></i>
          Spending weekends setting up a <strong>hydroponic system</strong> on my balcony — my tiny urban farm.
        </li>
      </ul>

       <div class="text-center mt-12">
       	 <a
      href="/"
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-black bg-slate-800 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-950 mt-16 transition duration-500 max-w-52"
    >
      <svg
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        width="25"
        height="25"
        fill="currentColor"
        class="bi bi-arrow-left"
        viewBox="0 0 16 16"
      >
        <path
          fill-rule="evenodd"
          d="M15 8a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5H2.707l3.147-3.146a.5.5 0 1 0-.708-.708l-4 4a.5.5 0 0 0 0 .708l4 4a.5.5 0 0 0 .708-.708L2.707 8.5H14.5A.5.5 0 0 0 15 8"
        ></path>
      </svg>
      Back Home
    </a>
      </div>
    </main>
    </div>
</Layout>

